    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Jiggly Cakes was founded by three siblings from Puerto Rico who wanted to share their experiences of different cultures through food. What started as a cheesy idea slowly became a reality as time went on. Early in their careers, one sibling studied and worked in high-end hotels such as the Vanderbilt Hotel, gaining invaluable culinary experience. Another sibling, a professional self-taught stay-at-home mom, always expressed love through food. The final sibling, a business mastermind, always wanted to do something meaningful with family. Together, they formed the 444 trio, bringing their dream to life in Jiggly Cakes.</p>
